EN: We wrapped the present very carefully.

ZH: 妈妈把宝宝裹在厚厚的毯子里。
EN: Mom wrapped the baby in a thick blanket.

ZH: 包裹着特制的巧克力的纸裹得很美。
EN: The paper wrapped around the special chocolate looks beautiful.

ZH: 他把自己裹得严严实实，保暖防寒。
EN: He wrapped himself up tightly to keep warm.

ZH: 裹着学习资料的包裹从邮局寄来了。
EN: The package containing study materials arrived from the post office.

